---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — BudgetSanta" description="Learn more about BudgetSanta.">
  <article>
    <div class="prose">
      <h1>About Me</h1>

      <p>
        Hi there! I'm BudgetSanta — a software engineer who enjoys building things,
        writing about them, and occasionally yelling at compilers.
      </p>

      <p>
        This blog is where I share technical posts, notes, and whatever I'm currently
        obsessed with. Topics tend to orbit around:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Software architecture &amp; engineering</li>
        <li>Web development (frontend &amp; backend)</li>
        <li>Dev tooling, automation, and workflows</li>
        <li>Anything I spent too long debugging and want to document for future me</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>

      <p>
        You can find me on <a href="https://github.com/BudgetSanta">GitHub</a>.
        Feel free to open an issue on the
        <a href="https://github.com/BudgetSanta/website">website repo</a> if
        something's broken or you have a suggestion.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
